1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:13:37.000Z","msg":"咁撚多警力, 721又唔見人?"},{"pid":"79f19afb753581cbcacfdc3b5c573c5226510d55","tid":1831893,"uid":237425,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:24:28.000Z","msg":"想當年旺角魚蛋起義係自雨革之後，最勇敢既本土派對黑警反抗戰<br />\n<br />\n係近年抗爭轉捩點"},{"pid":"54f9a174a55e923fca9f63f10f45905ab5185d98","tid":1831893,"uid":65449,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTJefxs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTJefxs.gif&h=b5544209&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d19194d132b378f8ea4f1d9145c2ed1c7491bb7","tid":1831893,"uid":3457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:27:42.000Z","msg":"咩呀 鄧炳強都話勇武拉曬 <br />\n唔會有勇武嫁喇 <br />\n撤退喇 <br />\n<br />\n成日話核心勇武拉曬 咪拉曬囉<br />\n冇勇武嫁喇 <br />\n黑警快撤退"},{"pid":"6d6cc0e59ee7065db15455b35eb82e4287095a4c","tid":1831893,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:29:26.000Z","msg":"留名等睇藍豬俾曱甴屎開年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9571dc911e45df644396f366fd3336e5108a7d","tid":1831893,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:31:11.000Z","msg":"咁姐係旺角部署左？"},{"pid":"a91e14b7947663c634fcb1daf265fa9e41daea49","tid":1831893,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8160a69b2e8ee97a1d9b33d29868db5f78c208b","tid":1831893,"uid":143499,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:35:08.000Z","msg":"我只會話傻鳩嘅白痴偽勇武先會按照對方嘅指示食鴻門宴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明知對方會set個主戰場喺旺角，人哋擺曬重兵放曬警察喺舖頭準備突圍而出你都要去，仲要次次淨係對持， 幾乎冇狗受傷，冇一粒汽油彈掉中恐怖分子，對方安然無恙 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有偽勇武都係金魚腦， 明明講咗半年每個post幾千正皮，講到明唔好包圍警署<br />\n<br />\n因為你企幾個鐘就攰，佢一出嚟你就死<br />\n<br />\n而對方喺入面嘆冷氣食花生睇廢青<br />\n<br />\n乜都做唔到畀人拉幾百人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聰明人就聲東擊西 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過好難講，你知啦，講咗幾個月....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n靜靜雞好似上次荃灣掟汽油彈燒咗佢幾架車唔好嘅， 太過暴力會輸民意 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係都要乜都做唔到，畀人拉咗先開心先有型嘅先爭取到民意"},{"pid":"7d09373135efb71957863ae445fc3a166d0886f9","tid":1831893,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:36:15.000Z","msg":"2000黑警本身都未係最大問題<br />\n問題係渣車，大量狗車，配合裝甲、水炮<br />\n佢地變相控制哂交通同地利因素<br />\n<br />\n如果果日真係黎料，一般手法肯定行唔通"},{"pid":"55a31285da31cf1f89d4a8b52a2ff20550c91401","tid":1831893,"uid":37058,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:36:38.000Z","msg":"旺角？狗宿會唔會高危啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警親朋戚友到齊所有香港垃圾齊集狗宿"},{"pid":"db3a0cf5616d908ca548f730e81e679e077b6d32","tid":1831893,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:36:51.000Z","msg":"好！<br />\n魚蛋新革命！<br />\n正式啓動"},{"pid":"02c8f29713fdfee6e86a759b4d4062f88ae75198","tid":1831893,"uid":126317,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f7d0c7d9812e47ec7bdc3771944e6678d15439fc","tid":1831893,"uid":201414,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:41:43.000Z","msg":"死黑驚 驚就縮番埋你老母個lone度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:39:34.000Z","msg":"實質班狗想年初人放假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果全港狗宿開花就大件事"},{"pid":"de56e6909801b78944a5abb69f1848869b8511ef","tid":1831893,"uid":126283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"766d32c08d7c7747f402f0da47d4799d472b5c9e","tid":1831893,"uid":35084,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"8f4da15ddddc4edf8f5b9bd5b7e50658071f2bf4","tid":1831893,"uid":12405,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:54:44.000Z","msg":"very good, 連和你shop都唔使搞 旺角都會變死城 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T18:09:47.000Z","msg":"放個垃圾桶係彌敦道，即刻2000條狗出黎堵路，